name: Brompton Enhanced Multi-Asset Income ETF
longDescription: The investment objectives of the Brompton ETF are to provide Unitholders with (a) attractive monthly distributions and (b) the opportunity for capital appreciation. Fund investing, directly or indirectly, on a leveraged basis, in a portfolio of equity and fixed income securities.
fulldescription: The investment objectives of the Brompton ETF are to provide Unitholders with (a) attractive monthly distributions and (b) the opportunity for capital appreciation. Fund investing, directly or indirectly, on a leveraged basis, in a portfolio of equity and fixed income securities. The Brompton ETF seeks to hedge substantially all of its direct exposure to foreign currencies back to the Canadian dollar
